== Other Interests 

I am interested in learning languages such as Latin and Sanskrit, through which I feel touch with ancient cultures that shape the way human beings are thinking and behaving; I enjoy reading books about Asian history and European history (those parts related to religions and society), philosophy, and art. I am also immersed in exploring programming languages with different design rationales, especially functional programming languages such as Haskell. There is more to talk. 'd love to make any friends that share those interests with me!!
